Invocation Name: hoosier heat radio
des: Will play Hoosier Heat Radio on Alexa devices. Hoosier Heat Radio is an internet radio station that plays hip-hop and R&B music, and also showcases DJ mix shows. Hoosier Heat Radio is based in Indiana and is part of the Fleet DJ Radio Network.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
